      "seed": 1124210046,
      "version": 485,
      "versionNonce": 1855218558,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1775679990849,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Reason for Dynamo DB ?\n    1. This is high availablity.\n    2. Not much complex relation here.\n    3. Can scale perfectly.\n\nOptional: \n    - Add a new table -> driverLock (TTL) for driversId.\n    - Remove the use of Redis for distribured lock.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Reason for Dynamo DB ?\n    1. This is high availablity.\n    2. Not much complex relation here.\n    3. Can scale perfectly.\n\nOptional: \n    - Add a new table -> driverLock (TTL) for driversId.\n    - Remove the use of Redis for distribured lock.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
